  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You raise your brawling or unarmed weapons to block. While raised, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to your AC. If an attack critically misses you in this state, you can retaliate with a Strike as a reaction with the blocking weapon with a +2 circumstance bonus to your attack roll. After this attack, you no longer block.</p><p>If you spend a focus point when you use this action, you gain resistance equal to your level. After reducing the damage from an attack, you can retaliate as above.</p>"
